Invocation Name: b. dubs
des:
Find out exactly when your favorite sports are roaring back to action. The Sports Comeback skill from Buffalo Wild Wings allows you to cut though all the rumors and confusion and know exactly when you can watch your favorite sports again.

To get started, just say, "Alexa, ask b. dubs when (your favorite sport) is coming back." It’s that easy.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
